	<h1 class="title">「万物简史」利玛窦的中国版世界地图</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/4696/small/4696.jpg?1418030328" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">苏琦 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-11-22 08:28:35 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/17905/medium/17905.jpg?1448095858" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


